description:
Chuck and Al are back with a new job...and another reason to get fired. In this episode, our favorite critics review "Santa Mesa" (A photographer takes a troubled young Filipino boy under his wing.") and "Zombadings" (gay zombies).

To watch Santa Mesa: (free on hulu)
http://www.hulu.com/watch/487231

To watch Zombadings:
